¶ Sweet Jane... ¶

39:50.715 --> 39:53.282
(indistinct chatter)

39:57.288 --> 40:00.356
(indistinct chatter,
laughter)

40:06.330 --> 40:10.265
You think they'll grow up to
be porn stars or strippers?

40:11.702 --> 40:13.235
My money's on stripping.

40:13.237 --> 40:14.570
It's free drinks.

40:16.006 --> 40:18.374
Those girls?

40:18.376 --> 40:20.042
They'll end up choking
on their own vomit

40:20.044 --> 40:22.644
before they hit 25.

40:26.484 --> 40:27.549
Halloween.

40:27.551 --> 40:29.985
It's for losers.

40:29.987 --> 40:32.755
Grown adults acting
like fools.

40:32.757 --> 40:35.357
Playing pretend.

40:35.359 --> 40:36.992
I like my life.

40:36.994 --> 40:39.928
I got a job that flies me
business class to L.A.

40:39.930 --> 40:42.398
Puts me up at the Bonaventure.

40:42.400 --> 40:44.466
(laughing)

40:47.238 --> 40:50.873
I don't need a Batman
costume to have some fun.

40:50.875 --> 40:53.442
And what's your idea of fun?

40:54.445 --> 40:57.479
Whatever you're selling.

41:11.529 --> 41:13.429
You should both be dead.

41:13.431 --> 41:16.965
Oh, no, he's not dead.

41:16.967 --> 41:18.066
He's the undead.

41:18.068 --> 41:19.401
I made him a zombie

41:19.403 --> 41:21.236
when I poured acid
in his brain.

41:21.238 --> 41:23.906
You're not gonna run
away from me anymore.

41:23.908 --> 41:25.908
I'm yours forever,
Jeffrey.

41:25.910 --> 41:27.709
(grunting)

41:27.711 --> 41:30.212
This, this isn't happening!

41:30.214 --> 41:32.648
I'm afraid we've
lost our detective.

41:32.650 --> 41:35.284
I thought he would appreciate
this dark evil,

41:35.286 --> 41:36.452
given the line of
work he's in.

41:36.454 --> 41:37.886
But John is clearly

41:37.888 --> 41:39.655
not yet our kind.

41:39.657 --> 41:41.256
Forget him.
I want to drink.

41:41.258 --> 41:42.424
To the master!

41:42.426 --> 41:44.693
Ah, thank you.

41:51.435 --> 41:55.471
Thank you all for being here
on Devil's Night,

41:55.473 --> 41:58.440
but it is I who should be
the one celebrating you.

41:58.442 --> 42:00.642
I look around

42:00.644 --> 42:02.811
and I see the definition

42:02.813 --> 42:05.614
of American success.

42:05.616 --> 42:07.683
They write books about you.

42:07.685 --> 42:09.551
Make movies
of your life.

42:10.521 --> 42:13.121
Johnny Depp likes my paintings!

42:13.123 --> 42:14.623
Years after your death,

42:14.625 --> 42:16.124
people continue

42:16.126 --> 42:18.427
to be enthralled.

42:18.429 --> 42:21.363
You've made your
mark in history.

42:21.365 --> 42:22.931
Like the<i> Iliad,</i>

42:22.933 --> 42:25.334
your stories will live on

42:25.336 --> 42:27.102
forever.

42:30.541 --> 42:33.542
I consider you all my equals.

42:33.544 --> 42:36.111
Nothing would please me more

42:36.113 --> 42:38.480
if you could stay and join me

42:38.482 --> 42:41.149
for dessert.

42:41.151 --> 42:42.951
(all cheering, clamoring)

42:44.989 --> 42:47.956
Dessert, almost forgot.

42:49.527 --> 42:52.461
I'm gonna go put
on my makeup.

42:52.463 --> 42:54.530
MARSH:
Ah.

42:54.532 --> 42:57.633
He's flying on an eight ball

42:57.635 --> 42:59.535
of China White.

42:59.537 --> 43:02.404
This will buy me a year
of being left alone, right?

43:02.406 --> 43:04.139
As always.

43:34.538 --> 43:36.805
¶ ¶

43:52.590 --> 43:55.023
To us,

43:55.025 --> 43:57.926
the greatest killers
of our time.

43:57.928 --> 44:00.662
This sacrifice
bonds us together.

44:02.232 --> 44:04.766
For eternity.

44:07.805 --> 44:11.740
(humming a tune)

44:11.742 --> 44:13.575
Pardon.

44:13.577 --> 44:14.977
(yells)

44:14.979 --> 44:16.044
(killers clamoring)

44:16.046 --> 44:19.381
No! No!

44:19.383 --> 44:22.651
No!

44:22.653 --> 44:24.086
John?
No! No!

44:24.088 --> 44:26.421
John! John! John! John!

44:26.423 --> 44:28.624
John, what are you doing?

44:28.626 --> 44:29.625
What are you doing?

44:29.627 --> 44:31.560
I need to help him!
Help who?

44:31.562 --> 44:33.629
The man you brought in
for them to kill!

44:33.631 --> 44:35.497
(shushing)

44:35.499 --> 44:37.265
There's nobody here, John.

44:37.267 --> 44:39.635
I don't understand.

44:39.637 --> 44:41.637
I came in the room
and you were alone.

44:41.639 --> 44:43.105
Crying.

44:43.107 --> 44:44.840
Have you been drinking?

44:44.842 --> 44:47.409
A little... at the bar.

44:47.411 --> 44:49.511
And they gave me absinthe.

44:49.513 --> 44:52.280
Oh, well,
that explains everything.

44:52.282 --> 44:56.618
You chased alcohol
with worm wood, John.

44:56.620 --> 44:58.720
You're hallucinating.

45:10.100 --> 45:12.134
Is anything real?

45:12.136 --> 45:13.602
(killers clamoring)

45:13.604 --> 45:14.870
I am.

45:14.872 --> 45:17.773
You have to trust me.

45:17.775 --> 45:20.809
I'm your protector.

45:20.811 --> 45:23.011
You disappeared on me last time.

45:23.013 --> 45:25.280
Oh.

45:25.282 --> 45:29.117
I'm not going anywhere.

45:29.119 --> 45:30.886
Come on.

45:30.888 --> 45:33.021
Let's get you
back to your room.

46:09.326 --> 46:11.960
¶ ¶

46:16.533 --> 46:19.167
COUNTESS:
<i> The transition</i>
<i> will not be easy.</i>

46:19.169 --> 46:23.772
<i> Birth is a painful process.</i>

46:23.774 --> 46:26.575
<i> As a mother, you know this.</i>

46:26.577 --> 46:30.011
Please.

46:30.013 --> 46:33.648
I can't lose my boy again.

46:35.753 --> 46:38.653
You must surrender
completely.

46:57.641 --> 47:01.243
And allow yourself
to be ripped apart.

47:01.245 --> 47:04.112
<i> Ravaged.</i>

47:04.114 --> 47:05.881
<i> You will feel</i>
<i> like you are dying.</i>

47:05.883 --> 47:08.216
<i> And maybe you are.</i>

47:08.218 --> 47:10.919
<i> But from blood comes life.</i>

47:10.921 --> 47:12.220
<i> Better.</i>

47:12.222 --> 47:15.157
<i> Stronger.</i>

47:15.159 --> 47:18.527
<i> More glorious than you</i>
<i> could've ever imagined.</i>

47:20.230 --> 47:24.065
<i> And you will rise.</i>

47:24.067 --> 47:27.169
And be reunited
with your child.

47:27.171 --> 47:29.738
For all of eternity.

47:34.077 --> 47:36.678
(gasps)
